OL,3,CRare heron caught on camera in Somerset
OL,5,FA type of heron rarely seen in the UK
OL,6,Fhas been caught on cameras at the
OL,7,FNational Trust's Holnicote Estate in
OL,8,FSomerset, for three days in a row.
OL,10,FBlack-crowned night herons are
OL,11,Fwidespread across Africa, Asia, the
OL,12,FAmericas and Europe, but not here,
OL,13,Flargely due to a 97 per cent loss of
OL,14,Fwetland across the UK.
OL,16,FThe first confirmed breeding of night
OL,17,Fheron in the UK was recorded in
OL,18,FSomerset in 2017.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
