OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1784908087
OL,3,CRare heron caught on camera in Somerset
OL,5,FThey grows up to 66cm in size, roughly
OL,6,Fhalf the length of the much taller
OL,7,Fgrey heron. They're mainly active at
OL,8,Fnight, making it doubly difficult for
OL,9,Fenthusiasts to spot.
OL,11,FBen Eardley, restore nature project
OL,12,Fmanager for Somerset Coast and
OL,13,FCountryside, said: "It's rare to see
OL,14,Fthis wetland species in the UK and so
OL,15,Fexciting that we have observed one on
OL,16,Four estate cameras on three
OL,17,Fconsecutive days.
OL,19,F"The UK has lost over 97 per cent of
OL,20,Fits wetlands through drainage and
OL,21,Fchanges in land management.
OL,26,@uD@TOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
