PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1784908087
OL,3,CRare heron caught on camera in Somerset
OL,5,FJack Siviter, a beaver and wetlands
OL,6,Fproject officer at the Holnicote
OL,7,FEstate, added: "We are continuing to
OL,8,Ffocus on wetland creation through our
OL,9,Fproject work, as well as letting
OL,10,Fbeavers modify and produce these
OL,11,Fhabitats at scale.
OL,13,F"If we can do this successfully, we
OL,14,Fare likely to see more wetland
OL,15,Fspecialists arrive at Holnicote, and
OL,16,Fwho knows ` night herons might
OL,17,Fcontinue to appear."
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOUyD@TO]
