PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1784908087
OL,3,CRare heron caught on camera in Somerset
OL,5,FThe wetland charity WWT lists the
OL,6,Fnight heron as a bird it predicts
OL,7,Fmight become an established breeder in
OL,8,Fthe UK, as ranges expand due to
OL,9,Fclimate change.
OL,11,FThe footage is one of several
OL,12,Fsurprising moments captured on the
OL,13,FNational Trust's wildlife cameras in
OL,14,Frecent months.
OL,16,FFive livestreaming cameras across
OL,17,FNational Trust sites have captured the
OL,18,Fbehaviours of barn owls, guillemots,
OL,19,Fpuffins, beavers, pied flycatchers and
OL,20,Fblue tits.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
